title: IEC-104 Over-Frequent Measurement Flooding (DoS)
id: xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx #Der x er hex (0–9, a–f), og y er 8, 9, a eller b.
description: Detects abnormally high ASDU transmission frequency from an RTU, indicating
  flooding, replay, or DoS conditions. Normal IEC-104 measurement rates are
  20–100 ms for polling and 300–3000 ms for event-driven data.
status: test
author: sigurdog
# date: xxxx/xx/xx

logsource:
  product: network
  service: ids

detection:
  from_rtu:
    source_ip|in:
      - "10.20.0.133" # SCADA slave (RTU)

  # Trigger hvis mer enn 50 ASDUs/sek (tilpass terskel)
  high_rate:
    event_rate: ">50/s"

  condition: from_rtu and high_rate

fields:
  - source_ip
  - destination_ip
  - event_rate

falsepositives:
  - RTU cold start bursts
  - Misconfigured RTU sending anomalous sample rates

level: high

tags:
  -